    <div class="services">
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Systemisation & Tagging</strong><br>Breakdown of asset register into systems & subsystems for structured completions tracking.</li>
        <li><strong>Inspection & Test Records (ITRs)</strong><br>Upload/create mechanical and electrical ITRs in Hexagon Smart Completions for execution & signoff.</li>
        <li><strong>Punchlist Management</strong><br>Log, track, assign, and close-out site punch items with live reporting dashboards and mobile workflows.</li>
        <li><strong>Pre-Commissioning & Commissioning</strong><br>Execution of static and dynamic test procedures in the field, with traceable reporting.</li>
        <li><strong>Turnover & Handover Packages</strong><br>Digital generation of fully traceable and signed-off completions dossiers ready for handover.</li>
        <li><strong>Field Mobility Tools</strong><br>Mobile-ready tools to execute, sign-off, and report field activities in real time.</li>
      </ul>
